<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link707942" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=707942&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F817061-i-read-the-children-of-hurin-but-when-i%2Fanswers%2F707942-in-the-appendices">flag</a>
