              <span id="reviewTextContainer3634839272" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8388639218875164299"><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/597790.The_Children_of_H_rin' title='The Children of Húrin by J.R.R. Tolkien' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Children of Húrin</a> by <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/656983.J_R_R__Tolkien' title='J.R.R. Tolkien' rel='nofollow noopener'>J.R.R. Tolkien</a><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1605118932ra/30365399.gif' width='480' height='272' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/>That&apos;s a very impactful tragic story which was set in the extraordinary world (Middle-Earth) Tolkien had crafted!! But Tolkien&apos;s classic writing was difficult for me to grasp the story and for that, I had to take some time to understand the tale better. However, the more the story moves, the brutal it gets. And this book is much darker, more depressing, more painful than the &apos;Lord of the Ring&apos;.<br/><blockquote>
  <i>A man that flies from his fear may find that he has only take</i></blockquote></span>
  <span id="freeText8388639218875164299" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/597790.The_Children_of_H_rin" title="The Children of Húrin by J.R.R. Tolkien" rel="nofollow noopener">The Children of Húrin</a> by <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/656983.J_R_R__Tolkien" title="J.R.R. Tolkien" rel="nofollow noopener">J.R.R. Tolkien</a><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1605118932ra/30365399.gif" width="480" height="272" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br>That's a very impactful tragic story which was set in the extraordinary world (Middle-Earth) Tolkien had crafted!! But Tolkien's classic writing was difficult for me to grasp the story and for that, I had to take some time to understand the tale better. However, the more the story moves, the brutal it gets. And this book is much darker, more depressing, more painful than the 'Lord of the Ring'.<br><blockquote>
  <i>A man that flies from his fear may find that he has only taken a short cut to meet it.</i>
</blockquote><br><i>Tragically beautiful.</i></span>
  <a data-text-id="8388639218875164299" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

